      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774593720813,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "place order\n\nUX + trust features (without backend)\nWhatsApp‑based order flow (no login)\n\nAfter “Place order”, show:\n\nYour WhatsApp number.\n\nExample message template:\n\n“Order: 101, Saree from Varanasi, Rs 1200, payment screenshot attached.”\n\nYou manually handle WhatsApp as your “order system”.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "place order\n\nUX + trust features (without backend)\nWhatsApp‑based order flow (no login)\n\nAfter “Place order”, show:\n\nYour WhatsApp number.\n\nExample message template:\n\n“Order: 101, Saree from Varanasi, Rs 1200, payment screenshot attached.”\n\nYou manually handle WhatsApp as your “order system”.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LjvMtCliAV030g6ehwzJ1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -726.7955214444158,
      "y": 559.0056080261464,
      "width": 1001,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
