      "seed": 1184692037,
      "version": 3,
      "versionNonce": 602514635,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774593741582,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Manual payment status (you manage)\n\nIn your own notepad / sheet:\n\nOrder ID, product, amount, UPI/bank ref, status (Pending / Paid / Shipped).\n\nYou can later add a “Order Status” page where user enters order ID; you update it manually.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Manual payment status (you manage)\n\nIn your own notepad / sheet:\n\nOrder ID, product, amount, UPI/bank ref, status (Pending / Paid / Shipped).\n\nYou can later add a “Order Status” page where user enters order ID; you update it manually.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
